commits.sourceNew: /** Checks the internal cache for an appropriate entry, and if none is found, * reads the terms/points in field and returns a bit set at the size of * reader.maxDoc(), with turned on bits for each docid that * does have a value for this field. * @param parser May be {@code null} if coming from the inverted index, otherwise * can be a {@link PointParser} to compute from point values. */ public Bits getDocsWithField(LeafReader reader, String field, Parser parser) throws IOException;
